*Nažalost* je već kasno. (Unfortunately it's already late.)
*Nažalost*, nisam mogao da dođem na vreme. (Unfortunately, I couldn't come on time.)
*Nažalost*, nije bilo uspeha. (Unfortunately, there was no success.)
*Nažalost* je nastala šteta. (Unfortunately damage was caused.)
*Nažalost*, nisu uspeli da završe zadatak. (Unfortunately, they were not able to finish the task.)